WEBVTT

00:01.860 --> 00:12.940
Presidente, prime ministeri, autorità, signore e signore, è un grande onore per me di essere qui con voi oggi.

00:12.940 --> 00:22.320
E mi piacerebbe dire di nuovo a Presidente Yusuf e a Presidente Lorenzo,

00:22.320 --> 00:29.980
come a tutti voi, per questa opportunità storica offerta all'Italia.

00:30.580 --> 00:37.360
L'invitazione di partecipare all'Assemblea del Presidente del Stato e del Governo dell'Unione Africana,

00:37.360 --> 00:43.620
il forum in cui l'organizzazione discussa le sue scelte politiche fondamentali

00:43.620 --> 00:48.360
e determina la direzione strategica del continente,

00:49.480 --> 00:53.660
è una riconoscenza che può solo rendere l'Italia orgogosa

00:53.660 --> 01:00.360
e che l'Italia accetterebbe con rispetto e un senso di responsabilità.

01:01.240 --> 01:05.800
È una demonstrazione di fiducia che non ci farà dissapostare.

01:06.760 --> 01:15.240
Ho l'onore di ledere una nazione che ha in selle delle caratteristiche

01:15.240 --> 01:20.000
che storicamente la rende un partner rispettato e valido,

01:21.120 --> 01:29.940
propensità per il dialogo, capacità per la discussione, rispetto per l'altro prima di tutto altro.

01:29.940 --> 01:36.900
Una nazione che ha costruito parte della sua identità e della sua politica francesa

01:36.900 --> 01:40.540
sul profondo significato di una guerra che, in volte,

01:40.980 --> 01:44.240
non è stabila e non è in grado di essere in grado di essere nostra,

01:44.720 --> 01:48.100
può essere la chiave per scegliere la cura.

01:48.600 --> 01:50.500
E quella guerra è cooperazione.

01:51.820 --> 01:56.080
La cooperazione di guerra viene dal latino, co-operare,

01:56.080 --> 01:59.000
a lavorare con.

01:59.720 --> 02:06.720
La vera cooperazione, cioè, non si vede mai un soggetto attivo e passivo,

02:07.780 --> 02:12.300
ma esiste solo in una relazione tra i quali,

02:12.600 --> 02:18.940
una relazione in cui le specificità di ogni uno sono indispensabili

02:18.940 --> 02:20.540
per raggiungere un obiettivo comune.

02:21.500 --> 02:25.980
Se guardi a qualcuno, non puoi cooperare con lui.

02:27.060 --> 02:31.860
Se vuoi planificare le risorse, non puoi cooperare con lui.

02:32.680 --> 02:37.560
Anche se vuoi dare una caratteristica, non puoi chiamarla cooperazione,

02:37.720 --> 02:39.300
perché la cooperazione è un'altra cosa.

02:40.300 --> 02:43.180
E cosa vuole l'Italia fare è cooperare.

02:44.700 --> 02:52.080
Ieri, insieme a molti di voi,

02:52.300 --> 02:55.100
abbiamo attenduto il secondo summit dell'Africa dell'Italia,

02:56.060 --> 02:59.560
il primo a essere preso su questo continentale.

03:00.300 --> 03:04.580
Voglio ringraziare il prime ministero etiopico, il mio amico Abiy Ahmed,

03:04.980 --> 03:08.340
e i leader dell'Unione africa per la loro ospitalità

03:08.760 --> 03:12.640
e cooperazione nell'organizzare l'evento.

03:12.640 --> 03:16.360
In questo contesto, abbiamo discutato cosa possiamo fare

03:16.360 --> 03:23.480
per migliorare e consolidare l'uno dei risultati più concreti di questa idea di cooperazione,

03:23.780 --> 03:26.340
che è il plan Mattei per l'Africa.

03:26.920 --> 03:32.800
Il plan di investimento che l'Italia ha implementato in diversi paesi del continente,

03:33.020 --> 03:36.360
in area ranging from infrastructure to agriculture,

03:37.120 --> 03:38.760
from health to training.

03:38.760 --> 03:42.500
This is a strategy that we have built together,

03:43.300 --> 03:49.020
because we do not conceive of the Mattei plan as an Italian plan for Africa,

03:50.100 --> 03:54.680
but as Italy's contribution to your agenda,

03:55.260 --> 04:01.010
with a particular focus this year on water-related projects.

04:02.180 --> 04:06.040
It is an open platform for putting our know-how,

04:06.040 --> 04:11.400
our technologies, our investments at the service of the objectives

04:11.400 --> 04:15.320
that the African Union has set out in Agenda 2063,

04:16.200 --> 04:19.260
starting with the creation of a continental free trade area

04:19.260 --> 04:22.000
that is integrated and prosperous.

04:22.940 --> 04:27.420
This is an ambitious goal which we support

04:27.420 --> 04:31.000
and which will require efficient, secure,

04:31.440 --> 04:35.120
and fast economic interconnections in order to be achieved.

04:35.120 --> 04:40.720
Like the Lobito Corridor, the railway and infrastructure backbone

04:40.720 --> 04:43.540
that will connect African markets to global ones

04:43.540 --> 04:47.440
and bring people, ideas, and economies closer together,

04:48.140 --> 04:51.880
a strategic project that sees Italy at the forefront,

04:52.340 --> 04:55.060
together with the United States and the European Union.

04:56.060 --> 04:59.520
In short, the Mattei plan is a comprehensive strategy

04:59.680 --> 05:03.700
that generates concrete benefits for our peoples

05:03.700 --> 05:07.360
and aims to continually expand its scope,

05:08.240 --> 05:15.140
relying on the irreplaceable contribution of major United Nations agencies,

05:15.440 --> 05:19.780
and I want to thank the Secretary General Antonio Guterres,

05:20.120 --> 05:24.200
but also the World Bank, the African Development Bank,

05:24.480 --> 05:28.580
and many other partners who increasingly share our vision.

05:29.580 --> 05:33.900
Two years ago in Rome we set out the course together,

05:34.860 --> 05:40.340
and in recent years we have followed it with consistency and determination,

05:41.060 --> 05:44.780
adding a new piece to the mosaic each time

05:44.780 --> 05:48.020
and bringing new nations on board every year.

05:48.900 --> 05:51.480
We have done so on many fronts,

05:51.840 --> 05:54.380
starting with what I consider to be crucial

05:54.380 --> 06:00.840
for building a true free Africa capable of determining its own destiny,

06:01.860 --> 06:03.940
addressing the issue of debt.

06:05.160 --> 06:09.300
We wanted to chart a course on this issue as well.

06:09.820 --> 06:14.420
Therefore, Italy has decided to launch a vast program

06:14.420 --> 06:17.220
to convert the debt of African nations,

06:17.840 --> 06:19.940
which includes, among its main points,

06:19.940 --> 06:24.460
the complete transformation of the debt of the most fragile

06:24.460 --> 06:27.560
and vulnerable countries into investments

06:27.560 --> 06:38.560
and the strengthening of the contribution to the World Bank's AIDA funds.

06:39.940 --> 06:43.940
Similarly, we have introduced specific debt suspensions

06:43.940 --> 06:48.360
which our intention closes into our bilateral loans,

06:48.780 --> 06:52.880
allowing African nations affected by extreme weather events

06:52.880 --> 06:56.380
to free up fiscal space to help their population

06:56.380 --> 06:58.980
and rebuild essential infrastructures.

07:00.240 --> 07:04.260
These are choices based on justice and responsibility,

07:05.240 --> 07:09.800
which are crucial for freeing up resources that are vital for development

07:09.800 --> 07:11.880
and for assuring peace and prosperity,

07:11.880 --> 07:14.780
including in those areas of the continent

07:14.780 --> 07:19.740
that are currently more affected than others by instability,

07:20.260 --> 07:23.580
insecurity and serious humanitarian crisis,

07:24.020 --> 07:28.720
such as neighboring Sudan and Eastern Democratic Republic of Congo.

07:30.100 --> 07:37.660
We also want our collaboration to be political at the multilateral level.

07:37.660 --> 07:44.320
We want to help strengthen the valuable work carried out daily by the African Union,

07:44.900 --> 07:50.960
ensuring greater consistency to the mediation activities carried out

07:50.960 --> 07:56.180
by the UN and the European Union and key international partners.

07:57.140 --> 07:59.780
We will continue to do our part,

08:00.180 --> 08:04.300
because we are aware that the future of Italy and Europe

08:04.300 --> 08:10.360
also depends on a secure, prosperous and peaceful Africa.

08:12.140 --> 08:22.720
It is often said in the many analysis of the troubled and complex times we are living in

08:22.720 --> 08:26.380
that history has started running again.

08:27.540 --> 08:33.080
This is true, and my opinion is that today it is running here.

08:34.060 --> 08:38.560
Africa is not a marginal chapter in this story, far from it.

08:39.040 --> 08:42.560
And those who do not understand this scenario are being left behind.

08:43.600 --> 08:49.780
But those who understand this scenario see the reality.

08:51.100 --> 08:55.240
A continent with a thousand peculiarities and a thousand demands,

08:55.580 --> 08:58.400
some of which are very different from each other.

08:58.400 --> 09:04.560
A continent rich in resources, raw materials and arable land,

09:05.160 --> 09:10.700
which can count on a decisive force in the age of knowledge, which is human capital.

09:11.960 --> 09:19.560
This is why Italy has focused much of its energy on training projects for young people,

09:19.820 --> 09:22.400
including in the field of artificial intelligence.

09:23.320 --> 09:29.080
In short, our point of view is that Italy and Europe cannot think about the future

09:29.080 --> 09:33.380
without taking Africa into proper consideration,

09:34.020 --> 09:37.020
because our future also depends on yours.

09:37.980 --> 09:45.140
Aware of this, Italy intends to continue to be a privileged bridge between Europe and Africa,

09:45.660 --> 09:50.620
making available the strength of its institutions, its great tradition of dialogue

09:50.620 --> 09:52.640
and the expertise of its companies.

09:54.060 --> 09:59.940
We want to do this also to achieve another goal that we all consider momentous,

10:00.480 --> 10:08.160
to guarantee the men and women of this continent a freedom that has often been denied them,

10:09.080 --> 10:12.460
the freedom to choose to remain in their country,

10:13.360 --> 10:18.620
to contribute to its growth without being forced to leave it,

10:18.740 --> 10:26.740
often paying unscrupulous traffickers to risk their lives in an attempt to cross the Mediterranean.

10:28.580 --> 10:36.460
Those who believe that migration is necessary and indispensable are in fact acting selfishly.

10:36.460 --> 10:43.240
If young people leave their land and their people in pursuit of the promise of a better life,

10:43.820 --> 10:49.560
what will become of the history, culture and existence of a country they have abandoned?

10:50.280 --> 10:54.160
These words are not mine, nor those of a political leader,

10:55.180 --> 11:01.460
but of a son who is proud of Africa and who holds Africa's future close to his heart,

11:01.820 --> 11:05.240
which is the Guinean Cardinal Robert Sarrach.

11:07.520 --> 11:16.580
Clearly, in order to guarantee the right not to have to emigrate,

11:17.440 --> 11:21.760
it is necessary to offer concrete opportunities for training and work,

11:22.540 --> 11:27.500
to enhance human capital and improve the quality of education,

11:27.500 --> 11:30.700
invest in skills and educational systems,

11:31.620 --> 11:41.100
and create industrial partnerships and joint ventures capable of generating stable quality employment in the territories.

11:41.880 --> 11:47.940
This is our mission, which is being put into practice in the many initiatives that Italy is promoting,

11:48.040 --> 11:50.160
including together with the African Union.

11:51.940 --> 12:04.620
What I would like to see today is in this solemn place dedicated to another great son of a free and proud Africa, Nelson Mandela.

12:05.480 --> 12:13.760
It is a great alliance between us to put training, research, university and innovation at the center of our common commitment.

12:13.760 --> 12:20.320
An alliance aimed not at taking away talent,

12:21.160 --> 12:30.140
but at multiplying it and building a model of development that respects people and values different identities.

12:31.800 --> 12:37.140
Presidents, Prime Ministers, dear friends,

12:38.200 --> 12:44.460
Pliny the Elder, one of the most famous historians of ancient Rome,

12:45.540 --> 12:50.700
said that something new always arises from Africa.

12:52.380 --> 12:59.080
So my wish for each of us is that something new may truly arise from today's meeting,

13:00.080 --> 13:06.260
something that no one expects or that many consider impossible.

13:08.460 --> 13:14.420
For impossible is usually the word that people without courage use,

13:16.420 --> 13:25.740
something capable of astonishing the world and suddenly making everything we have seen so far seem trivial.

13:26.140 --> 13:27.380
I thank you all.

13:29.080 --> 13:29.680
Thank you.

